window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>An action-packed new Isekai LitRPG Series from the bestselling author of <i>Reborn as a Demonic Tree</i>!</p> <p>Power up and become an unbeatable final boss.</p> <p>Damien Nightshade, a discarded royal masquerading as a Professor in one of the continent's greatest magic academies, is considered a mid-level boss—one fated to die in every playthrough.</p> <p>Now, I have transmigrated into his body.</p> <p>A game-like world has become my reality, and instead of being its hero, I'm cursed to die a pitiful death as a fated villain.</p> <p>But why should I accept life as a third-rate villain when I can strive to become the unbeatable final boss?</p> <p>Don't miss the start of this new Isekai LitRPG Series from Xkarnation, the bestselling author behind <i>Reborn as a Demonic Tree</i>.</p>"; 
